## PIPELINE

<a href ="http://processing.org/tutorials/pshader/">
Shaders
</a>
In Processing
```
uniform mat4 transform;
attribute vec4 vertex;
attribute vec4 color;
varying vec4 vertColor;

void main(){
   gl_Position = transform * vertex;
   vertColor = color;
}
```
```
varying vec4 vertColor;

void main(){
  gl_FragColor = vertColor;
}
```



